nks between knowledge and power, it sets new standards and guidelines to influence the measurement of violence in the coming decades.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 7aFAMILY & RELATIONSHIPS / Abuse / Domestic Partner Abuse.2bisacsh1 aBalderston, Susan, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aFrancis, Brian, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aHeiskanen, Markku, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aHelweg-Larsen, Karin, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aMergaert, Lut, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aOlive, Phillipa, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aPalmer, Emma, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aStrid, Sofia, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aStöckl, Heidi, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aTowers, Jude, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311119663340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781447332640zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781447332640/original  a978-3-11-119663-3 Bristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA